Highest Grade
=============

Steps:
	1. Take in the user input for grades.
	2. With these grades, append it to an array.
	3. Pass this array into a function as a parameter.
	4. In the function I will have a highest grade variable.

	5. Have a loop in the function that compares values in the
		 parameter array to see if the value is higher than what
		 is currently stored in the highest grade variable.

	6. Return or print this value.

